  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the protocol is to develop final draft PRO instruments of physical activity in
      daily life to be used and evaluated in the further validation studies measuring physical
      activity in chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
